```typescript
import { bus } from './lib/events';

// Subscribe
const unsub = bus.on('order.placed', ({ orderId, total }) => {
  sendConfirmationEmail(orderId, total);
});

// Unsubscribe when done
unsub();

// Publish
bus.emit('order.placed', { orderId: '123', userId: '456', total: 49.99 });
```

TypeScript will error if you emit an event that isn't in `AppEvents`, or if the payload shape is wrong. Add new events to the `AppEvents` interface as your app grows.

